00:26:58,800 --> 00:27:02,119
Um, and he-he learnt his trade.

569
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:06,399
And so, when he wanted
to... To direct second unit,

570
00:27:06,400 --> 00:27:08,119
um, they allowed him to do it

