I mean, you've got marvel,

1950
01:30:14,920 --> 01:30:17,119
you've got DC
doing all this stuff.

1951
01:30:17,120 --> 01:30:20,159
I mean, good stuff, great stuff.

1952
01:30:20,160 --> 01:30:22,319
But I think the live action

1953
01:30:22,320 --> 01:30:24,960
beats any of that stuff
hands down, personally.

1954
01:30:26,920 --> 01:30:30,279
-Nowadays, you get
specialists in to do the jobs.

1955
01:30:30,280 --> 01:30:31,439
I... fast and furious,

1956
