I worked on fast and
furious, which was great.

1957
01:30:34,520 --> 01:30:36,759
I mean, any... Any
stuntman in the world

1958
01:30:36,760 --> 01:30:38,919
want to work on
fast and furious.

1959
01:30:38,920 --> 01:30:40,239
And when I got the opportunity

1960
01:30:40,240 --> 01:30:42,879
through Greg to work
on it, I was over the moon.

1961
01:30:42,880 --> 01:30:47,079
Unfortunately, I didn't
get into the position

1962
01:30:47,080 --> 01:30:49,519
doing the fast-driving stuff,

1963
01:30:49,520 --> 01:30:54,519
because he got specialists in,
