1964
01:30:54,520 --> 01:30:56,279
and a bit downer
for some of the boys

1965
01:30:56,280 --> 01:30:57,839
because we could all drive.

1966
01:30:57,840 --> 01:30:59,599
I can drive as well as them.

1967
01:30:59,600 --> 01:31:03,559
But he wanted rally drivers

1968
01:31:03,560 --> 01:31:05,199
and people that
do it for a living,

1969
01:31:05,200 --> 01:31:08,959
which is understandable.

1970
01:31:08,960 --> 01:31:12,320
But a bit of a kick up the
old balls for us, you know.

1971
01:31:13,640 --> 01:31:16,599
-When I started, you...
you were characters.

1972
01:31:16,600 --> 01:31:20,039
You were brought in from extras,

1973
01:31:20,040 --> 01:31:23,239
and if you were able to do
something that was great.

1974
01:31:23,240 --> 01:31:26,079
Then you do stair falls,
then you start doing stunts.

1975
01:31:26,080 --> 01:31:31,079
Um, but we weren't necessarily
trained in anything particular.

1976
01:31:31,080 --> 01:31:33,919
So, we learned to do
those sorts of things.

1977
01:31:33,920 --> 01:31:37,639
And we, and... got away
with it all these years.

1978
01:31:37,640 --> 01:31:40,719
I wouldn't have got in
today in what they do.

1979
01:31:40,720 --> 01:31:44,479
