which is nice,
which is important.

1994
01:32:23,320 --> 01:32:25,119
But, you know, it's
a lot of us on the first

1995
01:32:25,120 --> 01:32:27,559
we just... We all
like a pound note,

1996
01:32:27,560 --> 01:32:28,599
and... and we want that,

1997
01:32:28,600 --> 01:32:31,919
but the job's always
