1998
01:32:31,920 --> 01:32:33,719
-I do think the characters
have disappeared

1999
01:32:33,720 --> 01:32:35,799
that were the Ken buckles,

2000
01:32:35,800 --> 01:32:38,879
Bob Simmons, George leeches

2001
01:32:38,880 --> 01:32:40,519
absolute... paddy Ryans...

2002
01:32:40,520 --> 01:32:44,039
Absolute incredible
natural stunt people.

2003
01:32:44,040 --> 01:32:45,079
-It's not as nice now

2004
01:32:45,080 --> 01:32:47,719
because there's so
much money involved now.

2005
01:32:47,720 --> 01:32:51,599
You know what I mean?
People sit and they're...

2006
01:32:51,600 --> 01:32:55,399
They're doing that at
lunchtime in the afternoon.

2007
01:32:55,400 --> 01:32:57,519
Where years ago, you'd
be pulling tricks on the guys,

2008
01:32:57,520 --> 01:32:58,999
you'd be doing
