2011
01:33:03,240 --> 01:33:05,959
It don't happen so much
now, and it was a laugh then.

2012
01:33:05,960 --> 01:33:08,399
[Indistinct] It's... We
still have a laugh now.

2013
01:33:08,400 --> 01:33:10,679
But, you know, when you
go into the dressing room,

2014
01:33:10,680 --> 01:33:13,999
everyone used to be
gambling or reading the paper,

2015
01:33:14,000 --> 01:33:15,759
or doing some work there.

2016
01:33:15,760 --> 01:33:18,439
They all sit there now,
they're tapping away.

2017
01:33:18,440 --> 01:33:20,279
See how much money
